First Class Tax & Consulting is currently looking to hire agents to do taxes, and the best part is, no prior experience is needed! 🎉

If you have a knack for numbers and are interested in starting a new career in tax preparation, this opportunity is perfect for you. We believe that everyone deserves a chance to learn and grow, regardless of their previous work experience.

As a part of our team, you will receive comprehensive training and guidance from seasoned professionals in the tax industry. We will equip you with the knowledge and skills necessary to excel in this field. So, even if you’ve never done taxes before, don’t worry; we’ll give you all the tools you need to succeed!

Joining us means becoming a part of a supportive and dynamic work environment. We are a tight-knit team that values collaboration and constantly strives for excellence. You’ll have the opportunity to work directly with clients, offering them personalized tax solutions and helping them navigate the often-complicated world of tax preparation.

At First Class Tax & Consulting, we provide our agents with competitive compensation packages and ample opportunities for career growth. We believe in recognizing and rewarding hard work and dedication, so your efforts will not go unnoticed or unrewarded.

So, if you’re ready to embark on an exciting journey in the tax industry with a company that believes in your potential, look no further! Apply today and let’s work together to deliver top-notch tax services while making a positive impact on people’s lives.

Email your resume to careers@firstclasstax.com or give us a call at (313) 816-2992 to learn more about this amazing opportunity.

Join our team at First Class Tax & Consulting and discover the world of taxes without any prior experience needed!
